Homey v2 REST API Endpoints @ http://<HOMEY_IP>/api/manager/ (?bearer_token=<YOUR_BEARER_TOKEN>)
https://apps.developer.athom.com/tutorial-Web%20Api.html

Endpoints:

# Devices
GET http://<HOMEY_IP>/api/manager/devices/device
GET http://<HomeyIP>/api/manager/devices/device/<device_id>/

# Drivers
GET http://<HOMEY_IP>/api/manager/devices/drivers

# Alarms
GET http://<HOMEY_IP>/api/manager/alarms/alarm/

# Zones
GET http://<HOMEY_IP>/api/manager/zones/

# Mobile
GET http://<HOMEY_IP>/api/manager/mobile/

# Notifications
GET http://<HOMEY_IP>/api/manager/notifications/notification/

# Reminders
GET http://<HOMEY_IP>/api/manager/reminder/reminder/

# Language and unit settings
GET http://<HOMEY_IP>/api/manager/i18n/

# Location
GET http://<HomeyIP>/api/manager/geolocation/

# Cloud state
GET http://<HomeyIP>/api/manager/cloud/state/

# Presence
GET http://<HomeyIP>/api/manager/presence/

# Flows
GET http://<HomeyIP>/api/manager/flow/flow/
GET http://<HomeyIP>/api/manager/flow/flow/<flow_id>/

# Speach output
GET http://YOUR-HOMEY-IP/api/manager/speech-output/

# Apps
GET https://<HOMEY_IP>/api/manager/apps/app/
GET https://<HOMEY_IP>/api/manager/apps/app/<APP_ID> (example: https://<HOMEY_IP>/api/manager/apps/app/com.fibaro)

# Users
GET https://<HOMEY_IP>/api/manager/users/user/

# System
GET https://<HOMEY_IP>/api/manager/system/

# Switch on:
PUT { "value": true } TO http://<HOMEY_IP>/api/manager/devices/device/<DEVICE_ID>/capability/onoff/

# Switch off:
PUT { "value": false } TO http://<HOMEY_IP>/api/manager/devices/device/<DEVICE_ID>/capability/onoff/
